## torrc — Tor Hidden Service config for synapse-tor
## This file is mounted read-only into the Tor container.

# Run Tor as a relay client (no relay, only hidden service)
SocksPort 0
Log notice stdout

# Hidden service definition
HiddenServiceDir /var/lib/tor/hidden_service
HiddenServiceVersion 3

# Forward port 8448 (Matrix federation/client) → synapse container port 8008
HiddenServicePort 8448 synapse:8008
